{"tid":1546203,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"死諫 x 太子事件 x 831","createTime":"2019-09-06T07:53:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T07:55:36.000Z","uid":300027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0917e36115dddbb32d82e69814bcbc7fe750dd61","tid":1546203,"uid":300027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:53:55.000Z","msg":"其實之前已經講過<br />\n<br />\n＜冒死進諫＞唔洗多講大家都知點解<br />\n<br />\n死諫，是指大臣為了自己的想法被采納而不惜冒犯領導者（通常是皇帝）的行為。常言有&ldquo;文死諫、武死戰&rdquo;，意思就是說&ldquo;文官應該為了堅持正義而不惜生命進諫，武將為了戰爭勝利而不惜生命奮戰&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n我明白一個都不能少<br />\n亦絕對不希望有多一位朋友犧牲<br />\n但要以死相脅就要用得其所<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>例如<br />\n如果港鐵(指明某人)唔係9月7日12點前公開831太子站cctv... <br />\n如果柒婆(那個人)唔係x月x日正面回應四大訴求..... <br />\n如果警方(某指揮官/局長)唔譴責警察濫用職權使用過度暴力拘捕&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n目標要明確一個人 唔好一堆過<br />\n行動再清晰 咁樣先有用<br />\n<br />\n黑鏡 x 勇武 x 和理非<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1419380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1419380</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"06cec3629c33b21055c2471319a547d488d26c9a","tid":1546203,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:54:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bae1d968d16d098573e7fbddba22c78dbc579e84","tid":1546203,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:54:42.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ade182be06586821f7af8c6c1072e1eeab2fc1a0","tid":1546203,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi